address2: 7th Floor No. 21 Wong Chuk Hang Road
longBusinessSummary: Meta Media Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily engages in the multi-media advertising business in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and the United Kingdom. It operates through two segments, Art Platform, and Digital Platform. The Art Platform segment engages in the sale of advertising space in the company's publication and distribution magazines, and periodicals; artwork trading, auction, art exhibition, and education; and restaurant operation. The Digital Platform segment operates a digital media platform, which publishes multiple digital media products and sells advertising spaces; and engages in production of customised contents for brand advertisers. In addition, the company engages in research and development; provision of advertising, management, and consultancy services; retail sales of imported books, and literary arts activities and exhibitions; and website development. It also invests in films; operates galleries and cafe shops; organizes photography exhibitions; and engages in the operation of online shop and physical stores for sale of photography artworks. The company was formerly known as Modern Media Holdings Limited and changed its name to Meta Media Holdings Limited in January 2022. Meta Media Holdings Limited was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Aberdeen, Hong Kong.
